ass todo put-tag - Put KEY:VALUE to the entries in RANGE in the todo.txt file

Usage:
  ass todo put-tag KEY VALUE [RANGE...] [OPTIONS]
  ass todo put-tag --help | -h

Options:
  --todotxt-file, -f FILE
    The location of the todo.txt file

  --verbose, -v (repeatable)
    Set the verbosity level

  --help, -h
    Show this help

Arguments:
  KEY
    Key of the requested tag

  VALUE
    Value of the requested tag

  RANGE...
    One or more RANGEs of entries to display
    Default: 1:

Environment Variables:
  TODOTXT_FILE
    The location of the todo.txt file
    Default: /home/lgrassauer/todo/todo.txt
